{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So, where are the robots?"},{"time":2000,"text":"We've been told for 40 years already that they're coming soon."},{"time":5000,"text":"Very soon they'll be doing everything for us."},{"time":8000,"text":"They'll be cooking, cleaning, buying things, shopping, building. But they aren't here."},{"time":13000,"text":"Meanwhile, we have illegal immigrants doing all the work,"},{"time":17000,"text":"but we don't have any robots."},{"time":19000,"text":"So what can we do about that? What can we say?"},{"time":23000,"text":"So I want to give a little bit of a different perspective"},{"time":27000,"text":"of how we can perhaps look at these things in a little bit of a different way."},{"time":33000,"text":"And this is an x-ray picture"},{"time":35000,"text":"of a real beetle, and a Swiss watch, back from '88. You look at that --"},{"time":40000,"text":"what was true then is certainly true today."},{"time":42000,"text":"We can still make the pieces. We can make the right pieces."},{"time":45000,"text":"We can make the circuitry of the right computational power,"},{"time":48000,"text":"but we can't actually put them together to make something"},{"time":51000,"text":"that will actually work and be as adaptive as these systems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56000,"text":"So let's try to look at it from a different perspective."},{"time":58000,"text":"Let's summon the best designer, the mother of all designers."},{"time":62000,"text":"Let's see what evolution can do for us."},{"time":65000,"text":"So we threw in -- we created a primordial soup"},{"time":69000,"text":"with lots of pieces of robots -- with bars, with motors, with neurons."},{"time":73000,"text":"Put them all together, and put all this under kind of natural selection,"},{"time":77000,"text":"under mutation, and rewarded things for how well they can move forward."},{"time":81000,"text":"A very simple task, and it's interesting to see what kind of things came out of that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87000,"text":"So if you look, you can see a lot of different machines"},{"time":90000,"text":"come out of this. They all move around."},{"time":92000,"text":"They all crawl in different ways, and you can see on the right,"},{"time":96000,"text":"that we actually made a couple of these things,"},{"time":98000,"text":"and they work in reality. These are not very fantastic robots,"},{"time":101000,"text":"but they evolved to do exactly what we reward them for:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":105000,"text":"for moving forward. So that was all done in simulation,"},{"time":108000,"text":"but we can also do that on a real machine."},{"time":110000,"text":"Here's a physical robot that we actually"},{"time":115000,"text":"have a population of brains,"},{"time":118000,"text":"competing, or evolving on the machine."},{"time":120000,"text":"It's like a rodeo show. They all get a ride on the machine,"},{"time":123000,"text":"and they get rewarded for how fast or how far"},{"time":126000,"text":"they can make the machine move forward."},{"time":128000,"text":"And you can see these robots are not ready"},{"time":130000,"text":"to take over the world yet, but"},{"time":133000,"text":"they gradually learn how to move forward,"},{"time":135000,"text":"and they do this autonomously."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138000,"text":"So in these two examples, we had basically"},{"time":142000,"text":"machines that learned how to walk in simulation,"},{"time":145000,"text":"and also machines that learned how to walk in reality."},{"time":147000,"text":"But I want to show you a different approach,"},{"time":149000,"text":"and this is this robot over here, which has four legs."},{"time":155000,"text":"It has eight motors, four on the knees and four on the hip."},{"time":157000,"text":"It has also two tilt sensors that tell the machine"},{"time":160000,"text":"which way it's tilting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163000,"text":"But this machine doesn't know what it looks like."},{"time":165000,"text":"You look at it and you see it has four legs,"},{"time":167000,"text":"the machine doesn't know if it's a snake, if it's a tree,"},{"time":169000,"text":"it doesn't have any idea what it looks like,"},{"time":172000,"text":"but it's going to try to find that out."},{"time":174000,"text":"Initially, it does some random motion,"},{"time":176000,"text":"and then it tries to figure out what it might look like."},{"time":179000,"text":"And you're seeing a lot of things passing through its minds,"},{"time":181000,"text":"a lot of self-models that try to explain the relationship"},{"time":185000,"text":"between actuation and sensing. It then tries to do"},{"time":188000,"text":"a second action that creates the most disagreement"},{"time":192000,"text":"among predictions of these alternative models,"},{"time":194000,"text":"like a scientist in a lab. Then it does that"},{"time":196000,"text":"and tries to explain that, and prune out its self-models."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200000,"text":"This is the last cycle, and you can see it's pretty much"},{"time":203000,"text":"figured out what its self looks like. And once it has a self-model,"},{"time":207000,"text":"it can use that to derive a pattern of locomotion."},{"time":211000,"text":"So what you're seeing here are a couple of machines --"},{"time":213000,"text":"a pattern of locomotion."},{"time":215000,"text":"We were hoping that it wass going to have a kind of evil, spidery walk,"},{"time":219000,"text":"but instead it created this pretty lame way of moving forward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223000,"text":"But when you look at that, you have to remember"},{"time":226000,"text":"that this machine did not do any physical trials on how to move forward,"},{"time":232000,"text":"nor did it have a model of itself."},{"time":234000,"text":"It kind of figured out what it looks like, and how to move forward,"},{"time":237000,"text":"and then actually tried that out."},{"time":241000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"So, we'll move forward to a different idea."},{"time":250000,"text":"So that was what happened when we had a couple of --"},{"time":255000,"text":"that's what happened when you had a couple of -- OK, OK, OK --"},{"time":259000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":261000,"text":"-- they don't like each other. So"},{"time":263000,"text":"there's a different robot."},{"time":266000,"text":"That's what happened when the robots actually"},{"time":268000,"text":"are rewarded for doing something."},{"time":270000,"text":"What happens if you don't reward them for anything, you just throw them in?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":273000,"text":"So we have these cubes, like the diagram showed here."},{"time":276000,"text":"The cube can swivel, or flip on its side,"},{"time":279000,"text":"and we just throw 1,000 of these cubes into a soup --"},{"time":283000,"text":"this is in simulation --and don't reward them for anything,"},{"time":285000,"text":"we just let them flip. We pump energy into this"},{"time":288000,"text":"and see what happens in a couple of mutations."},{"time":291000,"text":"So, initially nothing happens, they're just flipping around there."},{"time":294000,"text":"But after a very short while, you can see these blue things"},{"time":298000,"text":"on the right there begin to take over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300000,"text":"They begin to self-replicate. So in absence of any reward,"},{"time":304000,"text":"the intrinsic reward is self-replication."},{"time":307000,"text":"And we've actually built a couple of these,"},{"time":308000,"text":"and this is part of a larger robot made out of these cubes."},{"time":312000,"text":"It's an accelerated view, where you can see the robot actually"},{"time":315000,"text":"carrying out some of its replication process."},{"time":317000,"text":"So you're feeding it with more material -- cubes in this case --"},{"time":321000,"text":"and more energy, and it can make another robot."},{"time":324000,"text":"So of course, this is a very crude machine,"},{"time":327000,"text":"but we're working on a micro-scale version of these,"},{"time":329000,"text":"and hopefully the cubes will be like a powder that you pour in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332000,"text":"OK, so what can we learn? These robots are of course"},{"time":337000,"text":"not very useful in themselves, but they might teach us something"},{"time":340000,"text":"about how we can build better robots,"},{"time":343000,"text":"and perhaps how humans, animals, create self-models and learn."},{"time":348000,"text":"And one of the things that I think is important"},{"time":350000,"text":"is that we have to get away from this idea"},{"time":352000,"text":"of designing the machines manually,"},{"time":354000,"text":"but actually let them evolve and learn, like children,"},{"time":357000,"text":"and perhaps that's the way we'll get there. Thank you."},{"time":359000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}